# This repo tracks ONLY the files needed to serve the live machinedpens.info
# site(s). Backend pipeline scripts, credentials, generated source state, and
# internal docs are intentionally excluded.
#
# Strategy: ignore everything, then re-include just the published site files.

# Ignore everything at the repo root by default...
/*

# ...except this file and the Autmog site folder.
!/.gitignore
!/Autmog_Database/

# Inside the Autmog folder, ignore everything...
/Autmog_Database/*

# ...except the published site: page, data, and product images.
!/Autmog_Database/index.html
!/Autmog_Database/data.json
!/Autmog_Database/images/
